  <refentry id="function.pdf-open-image">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>pdf_open_image</refname>
    <refpurpose>Ouvre une image</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>int</type><methodname>pdf_open_image</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>resource</type><parameter>pdf-document</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>imagetype</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>source</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>data</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>long</type><parameter>length</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>width</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>height</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>components</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>int</type><parameter>bpc</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>params</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
      <methodname>pdf_open_image</methodname> permet d'acc&eacute;der &agrave; des images 
      de diff&eacute;rents formats. Les formats support&eacute;s sont : 
      <literal>jpeg</literal>, <literal>ccitt</literal>, <literal>raw</literal>.
      Les sources support&eacute;es sont <literal>memory</literal>, <literal>fileref</literal>,
      <literal>url</literal>. <parameter>length</parameter> est uniquement utilis&eacute; si
      <parameter>imagetype</parameter> vaut <literal>raw</literal>. <parameter>params</parameter>
      est uniquement utilis&eacute; si <parameter>imagetype</parameter> vaut <literal>ccitt</literal>.
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

